<i>♪ We are the Crystal Gems ♪</i>

00:03.549 --> 00:06.070
<i>♪ we'll always save the day ♪</i>

00:06.131 --> 00:08.203
<i>♪ and if you think we can't ♪</i>

00:08.205 --> 00:11.072
<i>♪ we'll always find a way ♪</i>

00:11.074 --> 00:14.976
<i>- # that's why the people #
- # of this world #</i>

00:14.978 --> 00:17.345
<i>- # believe in... #
- # Garnet #</i>

00:17.347 --> 00:20.148
<i>- # Amethyst #
- # and Pearl #</i>

00:20.150 --> 00:21.817
<i>♪ And Steven! ♪</i>

00:21.981 --> 00:23.674
<b>S01xE47 - "Political Power" </b>

